Method.ДеревоОтчетовПриАктивизацииСтроки.Comment.ИначеЕсли\ ЭлементДерева\.ТипСтроки\ \=\ 1\ Togda\nVariant\ Builder\.\nEsli\ Items\.GroupSettings\.TekushchayaStranitsa\ <>\ Items\.GroupVariant\ Togda\nElementy\.GroupSettings\.TekushchayaStranitsa\ \=\ Items\.GroupVariant;\nKonetsEsli;\nInacheEsli\ ElementDereva\.TipStroki\ \=\ 2\ Togda\nPolzovatelskie\ Settings\.\nEsli\ Items\.GroupSettings\.TekushchayaStranitsa\ <>\ Items\.GroupUserSettings\ Togda\nElementy\.GroupSettings\.TekushchayaStranitsa\ \=\ Items\.GroupUserSettings;\nKonetsEsli;\nInache\nNeizvestnyy\ Type\.\nEsli\ Items\.GroupSettings\.TekushchayaStranitsa\ <>\ Items\.GruppaPustaya\ Togda\nElementy\.GroupSettings\.TekushchayaStranitsa\ \=\ Items\.GruppaPustaya;\nKonetsEsli;.Description=InacheEsli ElementDereva.TipStroki \= 1 Togda\nVariant Builder.\nEsli Items.GroupSettings.TekushchayaStranitsa <> Items.GroupVariant Togda\nElementy.GroupSettings.TekushchayaStranitsa \= Items.GroupVariant;\nKonetsEsli;\nInacheEsli ElementDereva.TipStroki \= 2 Togda\nPolzovatelskie Settings.\nEsli Items.GroupSettings.TekushchayaStranitsa <> Items.GroupUserSettings Togda\nElementy.GroupSettings.TekushchayaStranitsa \= Items.GroupUserSettings;\nKonetsEsli;\nInache\nNeizvestnyy Type.\nEsli Items.GroupSettings.TekushchayaStranitsa <> Items.GruppaPustaya Togda\nElementy.GroupSettings.TekushchayaStranitsa \= Items.GruppaPustaya;\nKonetsEsli;
