Method.ЗагрузитьТекущуюСтрокуНаСервере.Comment.Если\ ЭлементДерева\.ТипСтроки\=0\ Togda\nSkhema\ Composition.Description=If ElementDereva.TipStroki\=0 Togda\nSkhema Composition
Method.ЗагрузитьТекущуюСтрокуНаСервере.Comment.ИначеЕсли\ ЭлементДерева\.ТипСтроки\ \=\ 1\ Togda\nVariant\ Builder\.\nZagruzitNastroykiVaniantaVTekushchuyuStroku(ElementDereva);\nInacheEsli\ ElementDereva\.TipStroki\ \=\ 2\ Togda\nPolzovatelskie\ Settings\.\nElementVriantIliOtchet\ \=\ ElementDereva\.PoluchitRoditelya();\nPoka\ ElementVriantIliOtchet\ <>\ Neopredeleno\ Tsikl\nEsli\ ElementVriantIliOtchet\.TipStroki\ \=\ 0\ Togda\nNashli\ Report\.\nZagruzitSkhemuKomponovkiDannykhVKomponovshchikNastroek(ElementVriantIliOtchet,\ Istina);\nPrervat;\nInacheEsli\ ElementVriantIliOtchet\.TipStroki\ \=\ 1\ Togda\nNashli\ Settings\ Builder\.\nZagruzitNastroykiVaniantaVTekushchuyuStroku(ElementVriantIliOtchet);\nPrervat;\nKonetsEsli;\nElementVriantIliOtchet\ \=\ ElementVriantIliOtchet\.PoluchitRoditelya();\nKonetsTsikla;\nEsli\ ElementDereva\.Data\ <>\ ""\ Togda\nChtenieXML\ \=\ New\ ChtenieXML;\nChtenieXML\.UstanovitStroku(ElementDereva\.Data);\nPolzovatelskieNastroyki\ \=\ SerializatorXDTO\.ProchitatXML(ChtenieXML,\ Type("PolzovatelskieNastroykiKomponovkiDannykh"));\nInache\nPolzovatelskieNastroyki\ \=\ New\ PolzovatelskieNastroykiKomponovkiDannykh;\nKonetsEsli;\nOtchet\.KomponovshchikNastroek\.ZagruzitPolzovatelskieNastroyki(PolzovatelskieNastroyki);\nKonetsEsli;.Description=InacheEsli ElementDereva.TipStroki \= 1 Togda\nVariant Builder.\nZagruzitNastroykiVaniantaVTekushchuyuStroku(ElementDereva);\nInacheEsli ElementDereva.TipStroki \= 2 Togda\nPolzovatelskie Settings.\nElementVriantIliOtchet \= ElementDereva.PoluchitRoditelya();\nPoka ElementVriantIliOtchet <> Neopredeleno Tsikl\nEsli ElementVriantIliOtchet.TipStroki \= 0 Togda\nNashli Report.\nZagruzitSkhemuKomponovkiDannykhVKomponovshchikNastroek(ElementVriantIliOtchet, Istina);\nPrervat;\nInacheEsli ElementVriantIliOtchet.TipStroki \= 1 Togda\nNashli Settings Builder.\nZagruzitNastroykiVaniantaVTekushchuyuStroku(ElementVriantIliOtchet);\nPrervat;\nKonetsEsli;\nElementVriantIliOtchet \= ElementVriantIliOtchet.PoluchitRoditelya();\nKonetsTsikla;\nEsli ElementDereva.Data <> "" Togda\nChtenieXML \= New ChtenieXML;\nChtenieXML.UstanovitStroku(ElementDereva.Data);\nPolzovatelskieNastroyki \= SerializatorXDTO.ProchitatXML(ChtenieXML, Type("PolzovatelskieNastroykiKomponovkiDannykh"));\nInache\nPolzovatelskieNastroyki \= New PolzovatelskieNastroykiKomponovkiDannykh;\nKonetsEsli;\nOtchet.KomponovshchikNastroek.ZagruzitPolzovatelskieNastroyki(PolzovatelskieNastroyki);\nKonetsEsli;
