Method.СкопироватьНаСервере.Comment.Если\ КопируемыйЭлемент\.ТипСтроки\ \=\ 0\ Togda.Description=If KopiruemyyElement.TipStroki \= 0 Togda
Method.СкопироватьНаСервере.Comment.ИначеЕсли\ КопируемыйЭлемент\.ТипСтроки\ \=\ 1\ Togda\nBazovayaChastImeni\ \=\ NaytiBazovuyuChastImeni(KopiruemyyElement\.Name);\nEsli\ BazovayaChastImeni\ \=\ ""\ Togda\nBazovayaChastImeni\ \=\ NStr("ru\='Settings'");\nKonetsEsli;\nNovoeImya\ \=\ SgenerirovatImyaServer(1,\ BazovayaChastImeni,\ KopiruemyyElement\.PoluchitRoditelya()\.PoluchitElementy(),\ Lozh)\nInacheEsli\ KopiruemyyElement\.TipStroki\ \=\ 2\ Togda\nBazovayaChastImeni\ \=\ NaytiBazovuyuChastImeni(KopiruemyyElement\.Name);\nEsli\ BazovayaChastImeni\ \=\ ""\ Togda\nBazovayaChastImeni\ \=\ NStr("ru\='Settings'");\nKonetsEsli;\nNovoeImya\ \=\ SgenerirovatImyaServer(2,\ BazovayaChastImeni,\ KopiruemyyElement\.PoluchitRoditelya()\.PoluchitElementy(),\ Lozh);\nInacheEsli\ KopiruemyyElement\.TipStroki\ \=\ 3\ Togda\nBazovayaChastImeni\ \=\ NaytiBazovuyuChastImeni(KopiruemyyElement\.Name);\nEsli\ BazovayaChastImeni\ \=\ ""\ Togda\nBazovayaChastImeni\ \=\ NStr("ru\='Papka'");\nKonetsEsli;\nNovoeImya\ \=\ SgenerirovatImyaServer(3,\ BazovayaChastImeni,\ KopiruemyyElement\.PoluchitRoditelya()\.PoluchitElementy(),\ Lozh);\nKonetsEsli;.Description=InacheEsli KopiruemyyElement.TipStroki \= 1 Togda\nBazovayaChastImeni \= NaytiBazovuyuChastImeni(KopiruemyyElement.Name);\nEsli BazovayaChastImeni \= "" Togda\nBazovayaChastImeni \= NStr("ru\='Settings'");\nKonetsEsli;\nNovoeImya \= SgenerirovatImyaServer(1, BazovayaChastImeni, KopiruemyyElement.PoluchitRoditelya().PoluchitElementy(), Lozh)\nInacheEsli KopiruemyyElement.TipStroki \= 2 Togda\nBazovayaChastImeni \= NaytiBazovuyuChastImeni(KopiruemyyElement.Name);\nEsli BazovayaChastImeni \= "" Togda\nBazovayaChastImeni \= NStr("ru\='Settings'");\nKonetsEsli;\nNovoeImya \= SgenerirovatImyaServer(2, BazovayaChastImeni, KopiruemyyElement.PoluchitRoditelya().PoluchitElementy(), Lozh);\nInacheEsli KopiruemyyElement.TipStroki \= 3 Togda\nBazovayaChastImeni \= NaytiBazovuyuChastImeni(KopiruemyyElement.Name);\nEsli BazovayaChastImeni \= "" Togda\nBazovayaChastImeni \= NStr("ru\='Papka'");\nKonetsEsli;\nNovoeImya \= SgenerirovatImyaServer(3, BazovayaChastImeni, KopiruemyyElement.PoluchitRoditelya().PoluchitElementy(), Lozh);\nKonetsEsli;
