Method.СформироватьНаСервере.Comment.ИначеЕсли\ Элементы\.ПанельРезультатов\.ТекущаяСтраница\ \=\ Items\.PageTemplateForCollection\ Togda\nVozvrat\ SformirovatNaServereVMaketKomponovkiDannykhDlyaKollektsii();\nInacheEsli\ Items\.ResultsPanel\.TekushchayaStranitsa\ \=\ Items\.PageResultCollectionXML\ Togda\nVozvrat\ SformirovatNaServereVVideXMLKollektsiya();.Description=InacheEsli Items.ResultsPanel.TekushchayaStranitsa \= Items.PageTemplateForCollection Togda\nVozvrat SformirovatNaServereVMaketKomponovkiDannykhDlyaKollektsii();\nInacheEsli Items.ResultsPanel.TekushchayaStranitsa \= Items.PageResultCollectionXML Togda\nVozvrat SformirovatNaServereVVideXMLKollektsiya();
Method.СформироватьНаСервере.Comment.ИначеЕсли\ Элементы\.ПанельРезультатов\.ТекущаяСтраница\ \=\ Items\.PageDataCompositionTemplate\ Togda\nVozvrat\ SformirovatNaServereVMaketKomponovkiDannykh();\nInacheEsli\ Items\.ResultsPanel\.TekushchayaStranitsa\ \=\ Items\.PageExecutedSettings\ Togda\nVozvrat\ SformirovatNaServereVIspolnyaemyeNastroykiKomponovkiDannykh();\nInacheEsli\ Items\.ResultsPanel\.TekushchayaStranitsa\ \=\ Items\.PageExecutedSettingsXML\ Togda\nVozvrat\ SformirovatNaServereVIspolnyaemyeNastroykiKomponovkiDannykhXML();\nInacheEsli\ Items\.ResultsPanel\.TekushchayaStranitsa\ \=\ Items\.PageDataCompositionResultXML\ Togda\nVozvrat\ SformirovatNaServereVVideXML();.Description=InacheEsli Items.ResultsPanel.TekushchayaStranitsa \= Items.PageDataCompositionTemplate Togda\nVozvrat SformirovatNaServereVMaketKomponovkiDannykh();\nInacheEsli Items.ResultsPanel.TekushchayaStranitsa \= Items.PageExecutedSettings Togda\nVozvrat SformirovatNaServereVIspolnyaemyeNastroykiKomponovkiDannykh();\nInacheEsli Items.ResultsPanel.TekushchayaStranitsa \= Items.PageExecutedSettingsXML Togda\nVozvrat SformirovatNaServereVIspolnyaemyeNastroykiKomponovkiDannykhXML();\nInacheEsli Items.ResultsPanel.TekushchayaStranitsa \= Items.PageDataCompositionResultXML Togda\nVozvrat SformirovatNaServereVVideXML();
